AN ACT
To repeal sections 48.020, 49.082, 50.327, 50.333, 50.334, 51.281, 52.269, 53.082, 54.261, 54.320,
55.091, 58.095, and 473.742, RSMo, and to enact in lieu thereof thirteen new sections
relating to county finances.
